<plot>This is the story of an urban educated couple, Tanvi and Nikhil, and their successful fast-paced life. This is also the story of Mohan and Gouri, who live a life far from the din and bustle of the city, far from the one lived by Tanvi and Nikhil; in the realms of abject poverty. A captivating story of a mother who understands motherhood through the birth of her biological child. The story moves from the busy streets of Mumbai to the desolate red-soiled dusty lanes of a village in Uttar Pradesh and brings to the fore the cross currents of human emotions and sentiments. It sheds light on those mothers who have always remained in the fringes of darkness.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?424200</url></doc>
